     §17 — MODERATION PIPELINE & CUTSCENE GENERATION
     ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
     PASTE THIS ENTIRE <script> BLOCK at the very end of teacher-cms.html,
     just before the closing </body> tag.

     DEPENDENCIES: Loads after §13 (episode save). Patches handleEpisodeSubmit
     to intercept the save and run moderation + image generation.

     WHAT THIS ADDS:
       • Text safety scan via Gemini before every episode save
       • Auto-generate cutscene image if text is clean
       • Flag/block and store evidence image if content is problematic
       • Email notification to admin on flag/block
       • Firestore fields added to episodes: moderationStatus, moderationReason,
